 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uinkiewiz.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Inkiewiz</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/15/02 8:01:42 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousetrainingstudioqafornewbies.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=14074.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.strike9.com/eq/file.aspx/path=/inkiewiz/fullsize/iriasmall3.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Recommended level and Thurg gate potion</span><hr size=1> Aye, it's a short quest based off the pottery skill, and the potion trivs at 122.  All the components you need drop in Crystal Caverns and Velks, and the quest NPC is in Thurg.  For more details, go to EQTraders and look under Pottery - Special Quests - Vial of Velium Vapors. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/udyllwindw.showPublicProfile?language=EN>DyllwinDW</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_star.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/16/02 4:06:46 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousetrainingstudioqafornewbies.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=14074.topic&index=8>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Recommended level and Thurg gate potion</span><hr size=1> And what's even better is the materials are all droppable (ie. sellable to merchants and PCs), so it is easily possible to get them at lower levels...<br>
<br>
Here's your shopping list:<br>
Drops:<br>
2 Small Pieces of Velium (stackable)<br>
1 Small Brick of Velium<br>
3 Crystalline Silks (stackable) (the silks, not swatches)<br>
<br>
Store Bought Items:<br>
2 Glass Shards<br>
1 HQ Firing Sheet<br>
<br>
You also need to get a quest container from a PC near the cleric guild in thurg.<br>
<br>
Good luck and good porting =) <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/usquinkmcpoke.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Squink McPoke</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/16/02 11:40:37 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousetrainingstudioqafornewbies.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=14074.topic&index=9>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Recommended level and Thurg gate potion</span><hr size=1> Whoever said you need good faction is mistaken.<br>
<br>
I'm max KOS to coldain and can do this quest repeatedly.  The only part that you need from thurg is the combine container, which is easily gotten via secret handshake.<br>
<br>
